{"tid":752763,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"夏日熱辣辣之自家衲肉火鍋","createTime":"2018-07-23T05:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T06:36:05.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2755a3ca08e674b3f4ff0dbc25d4f30eb88d3bdf","tid":752763,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:26:10.000Z","msg":"夏日熱辣辣 好熱好熱<br />\n同屋企人一齊喺屋企開住冷氣打個衲狗肉邊爐<br />\n食完之後中毒入深圳人民醫院 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：4大個蕃茄加少少胡椒粉做湯底，狗肉腸仔切粒，街市買新鮮冬菇狗肉餃子，冬菇切片，兩個烏冬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/23/132413_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F23%2F132413_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a71565f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11b28aba2e4c518e782a908228f03222bb616aaa","tid":752763,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:31:14.000Z","msg":"4大個蕃茄做湯底真係好夠蕃茄味，烏冬都索晒味<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcf839e5c570093523eb40fb417d78841a4b508","tid":752763,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad559f29f1d4ea3eaf5f76837fe1233d86383770","tid":752763,"uid":51057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"差d以為係老衲開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7c6a0fcc2837485310182333ccead20bb48dc3","tid":752763,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbcf839e5c570093523eb40fb417d78841a4b508","tid":752763,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"真打烏冬"},{"pid":"58b2a09e43809a73ac263b908947abce5cb5b59b","tid":75