ji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再俾佢聽到佢冇左一隻腳，我怕佢受唔住，喺深圳人民醫院出面咬死自己老婆之後自殺，客死異鄉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b73c3870c9e78edd9991249c518c260724c2890","tid":752763,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77743b01b34981c0ffa50515f5665484b3f96d01","tid":752763,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b73c3870c9e78edd9991249c518c260724c2890","tid":752763,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"雞蛋6隻，糖2茶匙，再加啲橙皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}